<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='185:193'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='193:206'>　五禮通考卷一百六十六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='206:227'>　　　　　　　　　　　刑部尚書秦蕙田撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='227:236'>　　嘉禮三十九</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='236:243'>　　　射禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='243:266'>通典漢石渠議曰鄉射請告主人樂不告者何也戴聖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='266:289'>曰請射告主人者賓主俱當射也夫樂主所以樂賓也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='289:316'>故不告於主人也宣帝甘露三年三月黄門侍郎臨<span class='krp-note'>失/其</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='316:342'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0087', 'WYG', '176-1b' );" name="176-1b" class="pb">[176-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='342:368'><span class='krp-note'>姓/</span>奏經曰鄉射合樂大射不樂何也戴聖曰鄉射合樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='368:391'>者質也大射人君之禮儀多故不可樂也聞人通漢曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='391:414'>鄉射合樂者人禮也所以合和百姓也大射不合樂者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='414:437'>諸侯之禮也韋元成曰鄉射禮所以合樂者鄉人本無</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='437:460'>樂故合樂歳時所以合和百姓以同其意也至諸侯當</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='460:483'>有樂傳曰諸侯不釋懸明用無時也君臣朝廷固當有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='483:506'>之矣不必須合樂而後射故不云合樂也時公卿以韋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='506:510'>議是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='510:536'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0087', 'WYG', '176-2a' );" name="176-2a" class="pb">[176-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='536:559'>　　　　蕙田案漢書儒林傳梁邱賀子臨為黄門郎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='559:580'>　　　　論石渠此云黄門侍郎臨者即其人也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='580:603'>後漢書明帝本紀永平二年三月臨辟雍初行大射禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='603:626'>通典晉咸康五年春征西庾亮行鄉射之禮依古周制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='626:632'>親執其事</span><br/>
